About Me

ENGINEERING INTELLIGENCE
INTO ENTERPRISE

I'm Aaron Benito Magana, a Full Stack AI Engineer who builds AI systems that actually ship to production. At Concentrix on Microsoft's Agentic AI team, I architect enterprise solutions that process thousands of support cases, automate complex workflows, and integrate with systems like SAP, Salesforce, and Dataverse.

My specialty is turning cutting-edge AI into business results. I've built voice-activated meeting assistants using OpenAI's Realtime API, deployed RAG systems that query across 5+ enterprise databases, and created intelligent routing engines that reduced manual triage by 70%. I don't just prototype—I deliver production systems with real ROI.

I also founded Bello Hello AI Solutions, where I bring enterprise-grade AI to small and mid-size businesses—from HIPAA-compliant healthcare chatbots to AI voice assistants handling thousands of customer calls. Microsoft Azure AI certified. Results-driven. Ready to build what's next.

FIELDTIME PRO

AI-Powered Time Tracking

The Challenge

Field workers at major utilities waste hours fighting outdated time tracking. Cryptic errors, wrong auto-fills, and poor mobile UX lead to:

  • Overtime compliance violations
  • Payroll errors requiring manual fixes
  • Supervisor bottlenecks
  • Frustrated crews, lost productivity

The Solution

A mobile-first app that thinks like a field worker:

  • AI Assistant — Pre-fills entries from job data
  • Smart PM Lookup — Field Service integration
  • Compliance Engine — CA labor law monitoring
  • Voice Input — Hands-free entry in the field
  • Supervisor Dashboard — One-click approvals

PM AI BOT

Voice-Activated Meeting Assistant

The Challenge

Project managers spend 30%+ of their time on meeting admin—taking notes, tracking action items, updating systems. Information gets lost between meetings.

  • Action items forgotten or lost

The Solution

A voice-activated AI assistant that joins Teams meetings:

ROUTE ASSIST

Intelligent Case Routing

The Challenge

Microsoft 365 support receives thousands of cases daily in 15+ languages. Manual routing is slow, inconsistent, and expensive.

  • 1,200+ cases analyzed per batch
  • 15+ languages (English, Spanish, German, etc.)
  • Multiple severity levels (A/24x7, B, C)
  • Complex routing rules to learn

The Solution

ML-powered routing with SAP comparison:

  • Language Detection — Auto-detect 15+ languages
  • Severity Classification — A/B/C priority sorting
  • High Confidence Routes — 90-100% auto-route
  • SAP Comparison — Validate against existing logic
  • Manual Review Queue — Flag edge cases

BARBERHOUSE AI

Voice AI for the Modern Barbershop

The Challenge

Barbershops lose revenue daily to missed calls, manual booking, and unanswered questions—all while barbers are focused on clients.

  • Calls missed during peak hours
  • No after-hours booking capability
  • Staff time lost to routine inquiries
  • Inconsistent front-desk experience

The Solution

An always-on AI voice assistant that runs the front desk 24/7:

  • Natural Conversation — Books appointments via voice in real time
  • Service Catalog — Answers pricing, availability & barber questions
  • Smart Recommendations — Upsells based on customer history
  • Calendar Sync — Direct scheduling system integration
